Infographic: Mumbai, Delhi airports 2nd best in the world 
7-3-2017 
Mumbai, Delhi airports 2nd best in the world

Mumbai and Delhi airports both tied for number two slot along with Singapore’s Changi to be rated as the second best airportglobally in the ‘over 40 million passengers per year’ category at the Airport Service Quality Awards 2016 conducted by the Airports Council International. The Awards are a global benchmarking programme measuring passengers’ satisfaction while they are travelling through an airport. 
